title: Japan Hopes for Frank Exchange of Views During Consultations in Moscow
text: Japan welcomes the continuation of contacts with Russia and hopes for a frank exchange of views during the consultations of the two nations' deputy foreign ministers in Moscow on a bilateral peace treaty and the territorial issue, Chief Cabinet Secretary Yoshihide Suga said Thursday. ...
